com.yworks.yfiles.layout.hierarchic

Interface ILayers


  • public interface ILayers
    This interface manages multiple ILayer instances.

    HierarchicLayoutCore creates instances of this class and passes them to the instances that handle the various sub-tasks of the layout process during automatic layout.

    Method createInstance() can be used as a factory method to obtain temporary ILayers instances.

    See Also:
    ILayer
